race.description: Harelec - Heat Of The Rising Star Handicap (C3)
race.comment: ROCKBARTON ANGEL (4) well drawn for this and can continue the winning momentum. Peaked fourth-up with a comfortable on-pace win over 1400m at Newcastle. Can handle the steep weight rise and take stopping again. DARK CHILL (2) was a month between runs when he shouldered the 61kg for a fading eighth over 1400m at Armidale. Can return to form with the claim from the good gate. Each way player. SPANDEX (6) capable on his day and can improve sharply at his third run back. Set a decent clip early before folding up in the straight to finish seventh over 1400m at Newcastle. Proven at the trip and worth another chance. HIGHLY TEMPTED (5) claim helps and not to be overlooked.
